graph TB
    subgraph "Kubeflow Notebook Controller"
        NotebookReconciler[Notebook Reconciler<br/>Controller]
        CullingReconciler[Culling Reconciler<br/>Controller]
        MetricsServer[Metrics Server<br/>:8080/TCP HTTP]
        HealthProbe[Health Probe<br/>:8081/TCP HTTP]

        NotebookReconciler -.->|monitors| MetricsServer
        CullingReconciler -.->|reports to| MetricsServer
    end

    %% CRDs
    NotebookCR_v1[Notebook CR v1<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    NotebookCR_v1beta1[Notebook CR v1beta1<br/>kubeflow.org/v1beta1]
    NotebookCR_v1alpha1[Notebook CR v1alpha1<br/>kubeflow.org/v1alpha1]

    %% User interaction
    User[User/Dashboard] -->|creates| NotebookCR_v1
    User -->|creates| NotebookCR_v1beta1
    User -->|creates| NotebookCR_v1alpha1

    %% Reconciliation
    NotebookCR_v1 -->|watched by| NotebookReconciler
    NotebookCR_v1beta1 -->|watched by| NotebookReconciler
    NotebookCR_v1alpha1 -->|watched by| NotebookReconciler

    %% Resources created
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates/updates| StatefulSet[StatefulSet<br/>apps/v1]
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates/updates| Service[Service<br/>ClusterIP]
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates/updates| VirtualService[VirtualService<br/>networking.istio.io]

    %% Notebook Pods
    StatefulSet -->|manages| NotebookPod[Notebook Pod<br/>:8888/TCP HTTP]
    Service -->|routes to| NotebookPod
    VirtualService -.->|routes traffic| Service

    %% Culling
    CullingReconciler -->|queries /api/kernels| NotebookPod
    CullingReconciler -->|adds stop annotation| NotebookCR_v1

    %% External dependencies
    NotebookReconciler -->|uses| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    NotebookReconciler -.->|optional| Istio[Istio Gateway<br/>USE_ISTIO=true]

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes /metrics| MetricsServer
    K8sProbes[Kubernetes] -->|health checks| HealthProbe

    %% Dashboard integration
    Dashboard[Kubeflow Dashboard] -.->|displays| NotebookCR_v1

    %% Styling
    style NotebookReconciler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CullingReconciler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MetricsServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style HealthProbe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style NotebookCR_v1 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookCR_v1beta1 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style NotebookCR_v1alpha1 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Istio fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style VirtualService fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#333
